social_posts.post_text: Another birthday doing what I love with people I love even more! 💛🥰🎂Thanks @Playbill for helping me celebrate - @songbirdstudionyc for capturing it all - and to my @aintnomobway family for the most delicious @baskinrobbins ice cream cake. #birthday #broadway #blessed #MyWishCameTrue #WeAreExtended #FightsNotOver #SaveAintNoMo

Yesterday was everything 🥰🎂❤️ Thank you to everyone for making my birthday so special: @playbill @baskinrobbins @songbirdstudionyc @akayedaniel @aintnomobway — and to these warriors for making the next week possible: @willsmith @jadapinkttsmith @tylerperry @gabunion @dwyanewade @therealsararamirez @shondarhimes @queenlatifah to other radical donations from @pinkycole @officialdhayes @matthewmichaellopez @real_sharpton @therealswizzz @deneebenton @domorisseau @therealdebbieallen 🖤BEST GIFT EVER 🖤 #Birthday #Broadway #AintNoMoBway #Extended #WeDidThat #YouDidThat #StillFighting #SaveAintNoMo #MakeRoom #letemwork

#2022 has been so good to me 🇺🇸📜💜&🧳✈️🖤 Here’s to more amazing views in the new year 👀

What an honor it was to be a distinguished guest at the first #Juneteenth Celebration ceremony held on the south lawn of the White House. Thank you to @potus, @vp, and @therealopallee for your moving remarks—and love to all of the performers who poured their hearts into an inspirational evening. Proud to have been a part of this historic moment with my #aintnomo family and grateful to @marvetbritto for making it all possible.

At the palace. This year’s @thetonyawards were held uptown at the @unitedpalacenyc. I still can’t get over how gorgeous that theatre was.
